Package org.daisy.common.xproc.calabash.impl

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CalabashXProcEngine
    Calabash xproc engine wrapper
    CalabashXProcEngine_SPI  
    CalabashXProcPipeline
    Calabash piplines allow to define and run xproc pipelines using calabash.
    CalabashXProcResult
    Implementation of the XProcResult interface
    DynamicXProcConfiguration
    This class allows to add new steps dynamically to calabash.
    DynamicXProcConfigurationFactory
    Mainly thought to be used throught OSGI this class creates configuration objects used with the calabash engine wrapper.
    DynamicXProcConfigurationFactory_SPI  
    MessageListenerImpl
    XProcMessageListener that appends messages to a MessageAppender.
    SerializationUtils
    The Class SerializationUtils holds a collection of functions to help out with the arduous task of serialising xml files.
    slf4jXProcMessageListener
    The listener interface for receiving slf4jXProcMessage events.
    XprocMessageHelper
    Collection of message formating function from the calabash dependent objects to strings
    XProcMessageListenerAggregator
    Aggregates a collection of XProcMessageListener rerouting the events listened
